---
title: Carb Smart Spinach and Feta Double Pork Patties with Lemony Tomato-Pepper Salad
description: Feta, lemon, sweet tomatoes and zesty garlic – this combo is full of bold, Greek-inspired flavours! Lots of veggies and extra protein from the feta add a satisfying spin in place of starch!

